	"content": "<h1 class=\"page-title\">Week 15</h1>\n  \n  <div id=\"todo-date-mount-point\"></div>\n  \n    <p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Overview</span></strong></p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: rgb(100.000000%, 100.000000%, 100.000000%);\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Fixed income securities and their valuation. Building replicating portfolios of zero-coupon bonds. Bootstrapping the spot rate curve. Portfolio risk management. Index futures and options</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Learning Objectives</span></strong></p>\n<p>Upon completion of this week, you will be able to understand:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>hot to value fixed income securities</li>\n<li>how to bootstrap the spot rate curve</li>\n<li>how to use index futures to hedge market risk</li>\n<li>how to use index options to hedge market risk&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Preparation for class</span></strong></p>\n<p>Mandatory reading:</p>\n<p>Lecture 7: <span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\"><a id=\"81603454\" class=\"inline_disabled preview_in_overlay\" title=\"Link\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/files/81706672?wrap=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-canvas-previewable=\"true\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/123249/files/81706672\" data-api-returntype=\"File\">lecture 7.pdf</a><a class=\"file_download_btn\" role=\"button\" download=\"\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/123249/files/81706672/download?download_frd=1\"><span role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"m1807.093 1482.47