	"contentText": "Week 15\n  \n  \n  \n    Overview\n\n\n\n\nFixed income securities and their valuation. Building replicating portfolios of zero-coupon bonds. Bootstrapping the spot rate curve. Portfolio risk management. Index futures and options\n\n\n\n\n \nLearning Objectives\nUpon completion of this week, you will be able to understand:\n\nhot to value fixed income securities\nhow to bootstrap the spot rate curve\nhow to use index futures to hedge market risk\nhow to use index options to hedge market risk \n\n \nPreparation for class\nMandatory reading:\nLecture 7: lecture 7.pdf\n    \n\nDownload lecture 7.pdf\nLecture 8: lecture 8.pdf\n    \n\nDownload lecture 8.pdf\n \nClass\nClass zoom link: Class logistics\n \nAssignments and Quizzes\nA7\nIB A2\n \nFinal Exam Preparation Materials\nStudy guide: final exam study guide.pdf\n    \n\nDownload final exam study guide.pdf\nPractice Final Exam: TBPS\nReview Session: Friday, Dec 5th at 9:00AM on Zoom\n \n \nAdditional Resources\nChapter 13\n \nClass Notes\nDec 2 class recording: \nhttps://cuboulder.zoom.us/rec/share/2r6XM8ZsOVryMuSkPvzTYSpPeKW8i-ZnzbHYU7FLHusiFEPlqSmUV_vQ0N8vxKVM.bvsrJtDsCZcN8FDr \n    \n\nLinks to an external site.\nPasscode: jLW02@+=\nClass work: Bootstrapping.xlsx\n    \n\nDownload Bootstrapping.xlsx\n  \n  \n\n",
